		<part id="pactices-api-lifecycle">
			<title>The API Lifecycle: Powered by OpenAPI</title>
			<slide id="openapi-changed-working">
				<title>How OpenAPI Changed the Way We Work</title>
				<ul>
					<li><em>Before OpenAPI:</em> API behavior often only documented informally or post-implementation</li>
					<li>Early tools focused on documentation generation from code comments</li>
					<li>OpenAPI enabled <em>design-first</em> workflows and <em>contract-driven</em> tooling</li>
					<li>New ecosystems emerged: editors, linters, test tools, SDK generators, portals</li>
					<li>OpenAPI turned API definitions into code artifacts not just documentation</li>
				</ul>
			</slide>
